{"tid":2414760,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"請教下有無狗狗中醫治癌介紹","createTime":"2021-02-19T16:03:12.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-07T18:28:23.000Z","uid":25750,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1bea104e3b0f8187383b80645e71131b09074579","tid":2414760,"uid":25750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T16:03:12.000Z","msg":"狗狗今年14歲<br />\n做過兩次手術切除，中間八個月食鏢靶藥<br />\n但都係有復發轉移左去淋巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n剛做第一次化療但個副作用反應好大<br />\n前幾日有敗血病入左ICU好彩最後無事<br />\n未做化療前生活一切正常，玩得食得訓得<br />\n做左化療殘哂，睇黎化療真係唔適合佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家只係想試中醫睇下有無得緩解下佢個病<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc837de39972e05eec632edc6232e0598e73ebf4","tid":2414760,"uid":25750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T16:04:48.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"176d7bb23b8e336539c505f845031c38f20b9370","tid":2414760,"uid":25750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T05:24:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ed841f96be366619879210c92c80695fa5f6c9a","tid":2414760,"uid":137647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T18:59:59.000Z","msg":"同你差唔多<br />\n狗仔本身有腎病<br />\n食藥會食到成日訓無精神<br />\n屋企人話呃錢後帶左佢去睇中醫針灸<br />\n睇左幾次同停左西藥即刻精神哂<br />\n中醫重講到keep住睇就可以咳走d病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n再兩星期後突然唔食野唔起身<br />\n又走番去西醫睇，話腎指數爆標，已經無得醫<br />\n過幾日走埋<br />\n<br />\n就算睇中醫都唔好停西醫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過我就覺得好多呃人啦"},{"pid":"ccf73bff3ad7ddac965631bb1ca52e2e8506b1b7","tid":2414760,"uid":25750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T05:17:45.000Z","msg":"我都唔係好信中醫呢味野<br />\n<br />\n但我狗狗屬於少數對化療有嚴重副作用果類<br />\n<br />\n所以只係想參考下多樣野<br />\n<br />\n睇下呢度有無人試過"},{"pid":"9405d3cab8a123ad817d7d7e5d7975097430a810","tid":2414760,"uid":833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T05:18:36.000Z","msg":"祝福<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咩品種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b5e03be85eefccc20782c47dc50048badadf4b8","tid":2414760,"uid":25750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9405d3cab8a123ad817d7d7e5d7975097430a810","tid":2414760,"uid":833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T05:18:36.000Z","msg":"祝福<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咩品種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T05:29:47.000Z","msg":"poodle"},{"pid":"2c6ed3bcaee60ed40c344f02018a1a6765948e80","tid":2414760,"uid":88471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T05:34:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52c8bb863685b8678b3d263e28ae2cb16a89ea10","tid":2414760,"uid":210347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T18:28:23.000Z","msg":"岩岩搵相關野睇下 睇到你2年前既留言<br />\n見到你狗狗仲係到少少感動<br />\n竟然起一起底去到2021年最新果個post<br />\n都講緊自己隻狗 你真係好錫狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我果隻今年都14 小學到做野<br />\n見到佢無咩精神 行路矇矇下咁<br />\n個心都好鬼唔舒服 成日驚佢有事<br />\n依半年內間唔中佢都有d就出事既表情"}]}